latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy 74th Independence Day🇮🇳❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
On the auspicious time of 74th Independence Day, I share a small clip of my talent round at @missteeninternationalind ✨
Appreciating the bravery of all wife’s of our warriors, The joy, the pride, the tears, the hardships, the separation, the skipped heartbeats, the uncertainty, the ecstasy. The army wives belong to a special breed. They are beautiful, talented, have gumption and are resourceful, in fact, not very unlike their civil counterparts. But yes, they are extraordinary, because they are in love with a soldier. A soldier who may never return when he goes on a field posting, defending borders, including the highest war zone in the world, the Siachen Glacier. The army wife remains in the shadows, giving her soldier the moral support, taking care of the family in his absence, loving him without any conditions, knowing that to him his first love will always be the country. Yes, this bold and the beautiful woman belongs to the Silent Ranks, she is an army wife.

Thank you for the video @dan.janvi ❤️

latestPosts.caption:
What a journey it has been!! I’m truly happy to return to the place where my journey began, back then in 2018 I remember reaching out to all the teen beauty pageants in India and searching for platforms so that I could live my dream but today with immense pleasure and joy I’m thrilled to tell you I was able to introduce my state to the one of the biggest national level teen beauty pageant  @teenindiaofficial the kind of feeling I felt when I traveled all around the country just cause there were no such platforms in my state I always said this to myself that I shall never let my people feel the kind of feeling I felt and try my best in creating the platform the state deserves heres to all the beauty queens in making from Sikkim the future is ours🥂✨ 
Good luck to the new queen @pranisha.07 make us proud. So many people have given me so much strength, inspiration and gift of my dreams answered. To my dear people my heartfelt thanks for your support and the space to learn and grow, and for believing in my dreams and aspirations, all the people I’ve met along the way will stay with me forever as I embark on the next part of my journey.
Special thanks to my mentor @melvynnoronha for always believing in me and fixing my crown. My friends and family and god for all the blessings that he has given me and for the rest of us.
Your first Miss Teen India Sikkim❤️
